     <div type="poem" subtype="to_the__reader">
   <head>Ad Lectorem.</head>
   <l>Scripta vide; monitus{que} caue: cupit ipse moneri,</l>
   <l>Sed non morderi. Neu fallat No<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>minis vmbra:</l>
   <l>Quaerito non a quo, sed quae sint scripta: faueto.</l>
   <l>Mente bona studui prodesse, fru<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>are: Ualeto. <note place="margin">Aug. ad Li<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>cent. Epist. <hi>41.</hi>
      </note>
   </l>
   <closer>
      <signed>Servus tuus peripsum, &amp; conservus sub ipso,
T. H.</signed>
   </closer>
